    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (*)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 14</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 14</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 30 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 18 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 34</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H, E *</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique works like Godai Taigeki: Shodan Jutsu, except you fire a devastating elemental attack, dealing 10d6 damage of the appropriate type. This technique has the following variants, each of which requires you have learned at least 6 techniques of its subtype.<br><br>- Chimetsu Daigeki (Doton) [Earth]: Material Focus At least 500 lbs of earth, stone or mud nearby.<br>- Hyoumetsudan (Hyouton) [Cold]: Material Focus At least 500 cubic ft of snow or ice nearby.<br>- Kougeki no Jutsu (Raiton) [Electric]<br>- Kuusetsu no Jutsu (Fuuton) [Wind]<br>- Shinryuudan no Jutsu (Katon) [Fire]<br>- Tsunami no Jutsu (Suiton) [Water]: Material Focus At least 500 liters of water nearby.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 1d6 per level or 24d6 (whichever is lower).</p>\n\n",
